<p>When I went to Snowbird in 2001 for the meeting that led to the <a href="http://agilemanifesto.org/">Manifesto</a>,
Jim interviewed me for the book he was writing on <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Agile-Software-Development-Ecosystems-Highsmith/dp/0201760436/">Agile Software
Development Ecosystems</a>. It provides a snapshot on my thinking
on extreme programming and this thing that a few days later we called
agile software development.</p>
